Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香和电蚊香都准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以为过一会儿就会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有消失  深夜的  最上川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说一寸的蚊子有五寸的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是放弃好了  乖乖地去睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这家伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了无谓的杀生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么打  不管怎么打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年每年都无法绝迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…这个家已经不能住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能搬家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为现在几点了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我安静地睡觉！
