Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:03.02,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N38
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰棒上的中奖出现在下面了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么反应啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  又吃那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话晚饭都吃不下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来因为冰棒中个奖就这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是没长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖写在下面可是超罕见的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也好下面也罢  中奖就是中奖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃几次总会中奖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  做小鬼真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是中个奖就高兴成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螃蟹啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是难得一见的超级稀有的东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留在最后慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士你这不是完全没动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你白天吃了一堆零食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  你吃了储藏柜里多少零食啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部！  你把这个月的份全部吃掉了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没夸奖你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为是阪本叫我吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为阪本说夏天食物容易变质的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和那个是两回事好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说点心是装在另一个胃里的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是过午休的OL吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么什么都当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全是被冤枉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说黑还是白  我就是纯白啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本你是纯黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  那是天生就长成这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再说下去也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士的草莓果汁我就没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃零食了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰棒中的奖我送给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会好好吃蔬菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把名乃的发条取下来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只允许你这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再犯  就一个月不准你吃零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有种现在给她的话  就会被她混过去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先把发条取下来再喝草莓果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就背对着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}没中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手是没中奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么东西都给我装啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有夸你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为博士你太随意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请三思而后行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有在听啊！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:29.41,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(1000,0)\an8}还算过得去的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去检索的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可能会出现
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美绪  正找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐正好有点急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你代替我去街道会的摊位帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这种事让妈妈去做就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和朋友去踢藤球了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看  有一万円的打工费哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:40.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}街道会大福展销会 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一万円的打工费真诱人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很闲  就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么超可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:46.74,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,300)\fad(0,600)}日\N常\N之\N39
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么鬼东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要陷入这种困境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:19:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且街道会的活动居然是两个人在街边卖大福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢脸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢脸了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路人都用可悲的眼神望着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能招来客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是吉祥物的大福君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有眼睛也没有嘴  只有一张白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都已经不是大福君了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是大福啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大福展销会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么展销会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全出局了呢  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  很痛的啦  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  下面没有戴护具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面没有戴护具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你们  给我住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样破坏大福的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的示范
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把这个取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想请打工的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻站着  去帮我看摊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  为了一万円的打工费  我就忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:21:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糯米粉  小红豆  和三盆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:21:00.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}和三盆：一种上等砂糖，产于香川县、德岛县等地，经常用于和式甜点的制作。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.51,0:20:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好想家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些真的卖得出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然摆得很整齐的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  这个一个多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说到底是多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  大福一个多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和三盆的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干呢  我才不用草莓什么的来做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费赠送
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  LUCKY
