Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云家今天也很和平
