Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まさか　いや　片思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:14.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an4}両\N思\Nい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やばい！　視線会合っちゃた！！！
