Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
